A nightmare, yeah.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:08.840
But I’m not sleep-talking.

00:02:08.880 --> 00:02:10.479
And my name’s not Worradej.

00:02:10.639 --> 00:02:12.000
I’m going home.

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:13.360
Where are you going?

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:15.480
I’m going home too.

00:02:15.880 --> 00:02:16.880
But…

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:19.000
I don’t even know how to get back

00:02:19.040 --> 00:02:20.760
or where to go.

