Life’s already hard enough
being a trans woman.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:28.960
And now I gotta deal
with all this too.

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:33.600
You don’t have a home
to return to now.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:36.240
Lord Singhanakhon’s ship

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:39.000
was dismantled to use the wood
for building the pier.

00:02:39.240 --> 00:02:42.720
All the treasures were sold off
and given to the villagers.

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:45.320
In fact, you as the Count’s child

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:47.640
were sentenced to forced labor.

00:02:48.840 --> 00:02:51.040
But it was me who brought you here.

00:02:53.720 --> 00:02:55.040
Kosol.

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:57.000
Tell me honestly.

00:02:57.079 --> 00:02:59.000
Your mission with Banjong,

00:02:59.160 --> 00:03:00.560
what else are you planning?

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:02.360
Can you tell me, please?

00:03:02.440 --> 00:03:04.600
Tell me, please. Tell me.

00:03:04.960 --> 00:03:06.840
Didn’t you hear
what King Chaiyached said?

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.520
That our next mission
is to storm the capital

00:03:09.600 --> 00:03:12.440
and take down Somdet Saenyakorn,
who’s seized power.

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:14.160
And if we succeed,

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:17.440
we’ll be able to change the law.

00:03:17.480 --> 00:03:18.760
And you

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:21.600
