00:03:56.680 --> 00:03:58.400
Don’t… talk… talk…

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:04.040
Talk. Talk.

00:04:04.280 --> 00:04:06.520
Talk first.

00:04:14.480 --> 00:04:17.760
