00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:46.400
Now,

00:04:46.440 --> 00:04:50.480
Lord Singhanakhon has been stripped
of his rank and position as governor.

00:04:50.920 --> 00:04:54.560
The city of Singhanakhon is under
Lord Kosol and the Revolutionary Council.

00:04:55.200 --> 00:04:56.760
King Chaiyached

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:59.240
