against your birth gender.

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:23.960
You’re a man.

00:06:24.280 --> 00:06:27.000
You can’t be exclaiming
ka, kha like that.

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:28.760
Yes, Teacher.

00:06:28.840 --> 00:06:31.840
Then I’ll be careful from now on.

00:06:33.040 --> 00:06:34.760
Naiyapinyapat.

00:06:34.840 --> 00:06:36.720
What now, Teacher?

00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:39.200
That hairclip, take it off too.

00:06:42.080 --> 00:06:43.720
This law,

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:46.600
this very law was enacted
in the Thanapura Kingdom

00:06:46.640 --> 00:06:48.640
by Somdet Saenyakorn

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:51.200
and has been enforced ever since.

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:53.920
Nong Phin, we heard that today

00:06:53.960 --> 00:06:58.240
you have something important
to announce to your fans?

00:06:58.320 --> 00:07:00.240
Yes, it’s…

00:07:00.400 --> 00:07:02.640
something that’s been weighing
on me for a long time,

00:07:02.680 --> 00:07:04.120
