the idol industry.

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:06.360
And today I feel like

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:09.480
I don’t need to hide this any longer.

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:13.920
I’m going to announce
to everyone that…

00:07:15.640 --> 00:07:17.200
I…

00:07:26.520 --> 00:07:30.120
am a trans woman.

00:07:34.960 --> 00:07:37.040
And from now on,

00:07:37.080 --> 00:07:39.840
