00:07:41.159 --> 00:07:43.600
Say it together, Prince.

00:07:43.640 --> 00:07:45.240
Prince.

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:48.320
I’ll stop lying to myself
and to everyone.

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:51.560
I’ll shine and show the world

00:07:51.640 --> 00:07:55.800
the most fabulous version of me.

00:07:56.720 --> 00:07:59.400
Nong Phin, don’t. Please don’t.

00:07:59.400 --> 00:08:00.600
You’ll get in trouble.

00:08:01.160 --> 00:08:03.280
Then let me face it.

00:08:03.320 --> 00:08:05.960
If our country still has
laws like these,

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:08.400
even if it’s a court order
or an arrest warrant,

00:08:08.520 --> 00:08:10.280
I’ll gladly take it.

00:08:10.360 --> 00:08:14.280
Better than losing my true self.

00:08:14.360 --> 00:08:15.600
All of us…

00:08:15.600 --> 00:08:18.880
We all have the right
to be ourselves.

00:08:18.920 --> 00:08:24.080
And everyone has the right
to be beautiful.

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:28.240
He’s the first to spark
a revolution in the idol scene.

00:08:28.280 --> 00:08:32.400
The first LGBTQ+ idol
in the nation of Saenya.

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:37.600
Give it up for Prince
and his fearless courage.

00:08:42.960 --> 00:08:44.600
Come to think of it,

00:08:44.760 --> 00:08:47.640
I guess I’ve got a streak
of rebellion in me too.

00:08:47.960 --> 00:08:51.520
If today we could take down
Somdet Saenyakorn,

00:08:51.560 --> 00:08:55.160
we’d abolish the anti-trans law
from this country right away.

00:08:55.320 --> 00:08:59.200
So trans women won’t keep suffering
under it for hundreds of years.

00:08:59.720 --> 00:09:02.200
Including me, in the future.

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:07.280
That would be so fabulous.

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:27.000
Mumu.

