00:10:06.800 --> 00:10:07.920
Fresh.

00:10:08.160 --> 00:10:09.880
Eat up, sweetie.

00:10:09.920 --> 00:10:12.120
Yummy, go on.

00:10:15.200 --> 00:10:16.560
I’ll feed you.

00:10:16.560 --> 00:10:17.680
Let me feed you.

00:10:24.760 --> 00:10:25.760
Eat.

00:10:26.160 --> 00:10:27.480
Eat.

00:10:33.240 --> 00:10:36.080
Good job.

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:38.120
One more piece.

00:10:38.120 --> 00:10:40.960
Yummy, good boy.

00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:43.400
Good boy, yummy.

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:46.000
Yummy, good boy.

