Good boy, so clever.

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:51.080
We’re friends now.

00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:52.720
Friends.

00:10:52.760 --> 00:10:55.080
Don’t eat me, okay, Mumu?

00:11:16.360 --> 00:11:17.640
Brother Banjong.

00:11:22.240 --> 00:11:24.640
Brother Kosol has already
toppled the Count.

00:11:24.840 --> 00:11:26.440
Why are you still so tense?

00:11:26.880 --> 00:11:28.720
This overthrow,

00:11:29.160 --> 00:11:30.520
besides the Count

00:11:30.800 --> 00:11:32.960
and the soldiers loyal to him,

00:11:33.760 --> 00:11:35.440
dragged others into prison too.

00:11:36.640 --> 00:11:38.080
That includes the servants
in the household.

00:11:38.760 --> 00:11:40.400
They knew nothing at all.

00:11:40.840 --> 00:11:42.840
They had nothing to do
with the Count’s rebellion.

00:11:43.280 --> 00:11:45.040
Yet they had to suffer too.

00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:52.120
Are you worried about the servants,
or about Worradej?

00:11:52.960 --> 00:11:56.040
Don’t forget, Worradej is
the Count’s own flesh and blood.

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:58.680
Worradej is with Kosol.

00:11:59.960 --> 00:12:00.960
I’m not worried.

00:12:38.520 --> 00:12:39.960
Kosol.

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:46.920
What?

00:12:47.280 --> 00:12:48.640
What are you doing here?

00:12:48.720 --> 00:12:50.880
If the officials see you,
they’ll send you to dig canals.

00:12:51.640 --> 00:12:55.040
I’ve been stuck in my room
for three days. It reeks.

00:12:55.520 --> 00:12:57.160
But the reason I came here

00:12:57.200 --> 00:13:00.000
is because I have something
important to tell you.

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:01.160
I promise

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:02.960
you’ll be glad to hear it.

00:13:03.520 --> 00:13:04.840
You’re here to confess
your love to me?

00:13:05.280 --> 00:13:06.920
Oh, no. Of course not.

00:13:07.560 --> 00:13:09.720
The reason I came here

00:13:09.800 --> 00:13:10.920
is because

00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:13.920
after thinking it over and over,

00:13:14.160 --> 00:13:16.040
if we want to make the world
a better place,

00:13:16.120 --> 00:13:19.120
we should start taking action from today.

00:13:19.240 --> 00:13:20.560
So I’ve decided

00:13:20.560 --> 00:13:23.280
that I’ll fight alongside you.

00:13:24.040 --> 00:13:26.040
But on one condition.

00:13:26.080 --> 00:13:28.280
You have to promise me first,

00:13:28.280 --> 00:13:31.120
once you bring down
Somdet Saenyakorn,

00:13:31.240 --> 00:13:34.800
you’ll abolish the law
that punishes same-sex love.

00:13:35.600 --> 00:13:36.720
Of course.

00:13:36.960 --> 00:13:38.600
That very law

00:13:38.760 --> 00:13:40.960
was the reason I was removed
as Regent,

00:13:41.120 --> 00:13:42.200
kept from being King,

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:44.440
and thrown into prison for years.

00:13:44.720 --> 00:13:45.720
Fabulous.

00:13:46.400 --> 00:13:48.560
We’re on the same page.

00:13:48.800 --> 00:13:50.400
Shake on it.

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:58.560
And I’ll propose another new law.

00:13:58.960 --> 00:14:00.240
What law?

00:14:00.960 --> 00:14:03.600
Legalizing same-sex marriage.

00:14:04.720 --> 00:14:07.000
And who will you marry then?

00:14:07.640 --> 00:14:08.880
Isn’t it obvious?

00:14:09.080 --> 00:14:10.640
There’s only one person.

00:14:11.800 --> 00:14:12.800
You.

00:14:31.680 --> 00:14:33.320
So, Your Majesty, here you are.

00:14:37.160 --> 00:14:40.160
Well, this toy is convenient,
isn’t it, My Lord?

00:14:40.240 --> 00:14:42.720
No need to call out and tire yourself.

00:14:43.560 --> 00:14:45.600
You’ve been with my brother
for three days.

00:14:45.640 --> 00:14:47.160
You look exhausted.

00:14:47.480 --> 00:14:49.560
Seems my brother really wore you out.

00:14:49.600 --> 00:14:51.720
Please don’t tease me like that, My Lord.

00:14:52.040 --> 00:14:55.080
I’m still a man, My Lord.
This is embarrassing.

00:14:55.240 --> 00:14:56.800
But at the Fire Crossing Ritual,

00:14:56.960 --> 00:14:59.120
