00:16:13.200 --> 00:16:15.280
Let me handle this instead, My Lord.

00:16:15.400 --> 00:16:17.560
Once I know something, I’ll send word.

00:16:18.400 --> 00:16:19.400
I’ll take my leave, My Lord.

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:26.840
